   There is a list of customers and new customers is addes to this list ,when they make an order first time.
   The customer's phone number is used to identify to differenciate new and old customers.
   The order consists of one or more pizzas.
   Each pizza can have ingredients from a given list, according to customer's request.
   There are different categories of ingredients and also min and max limit for choise of ingredients.
   For each customer, there is a order history and customer can choose thier most favourite pizza.
   The total prize of the order is calculated and shown
   Finally, sales are recorded.
   
